1116
01:09:49,993 --> 01:09:51,654
Oh, it's so beautiful!

1117
01:09:52,196 --> 01:09:55,222
-Madge Turner. l'm head of it all.
-Hello, Madge!

1118
01:09:55,432 --> 01:09:57,696
