Thank you so much.
l'm sort of embarrassed.

1139
01:11:03,600 --> 01:11:05,227
Look at this.

1140
01:11:05,969 --> 01:11:08,096
What a surprise!

1141
01:11:08,839 --> 01:11:10,739
Thank you!

1142
01:11:11,308 --> 01:11:15,142
lt's so nice to be back
in Los Angeles again.

1143
01:11:16,280 --> 01:11:18,510
All right, that's enough.
Thank you. Stop.

1144
01:11:18,749 --> 01:11:21,946
Really, you have to stop. Thanks.
All right, anyway....

1145
01:11:23,987 --> 01:11:26,182
l'm so excited to be here.

1146
01:11:26,456 --> 01:11:30,017
l was on the plane going over my speech,
the speech l always give...

1147
01:11:30,260 --> 01:11:34,253
...and of course l talk about
Georgia, my magazine...

1148
01:11:34,498 --> 01:11:38,298
...which is about to celebrate
its fifth anniversary.

1149
01:11:38,502 --> 01:11:40,265
Can you believe that?

1150
01:11:42,539 --> 01:11:45,736
l was going to talk about
the issue of face-lifts;

1151
01:11:45,943 --> 01:11:47,535
To do or not to do.

1152
01:11:48,812 --> 01:11:50,074
About aging.

1153
01:11:50,681 --> 01:11:52,979
About the fact that
it's okay to age...

1154
01:11:53,183 --> 01:11:55,174
...but, of course,
l don't believe that.

1155
01:11:56,353 --> 01:11:59,151
Anyway, l was sitting
on the plane and...

1156
01:11:59,790 --> 01:12:02,520
...l realized l didn't want
to talk about any of that...

1157
01:12:02,726 --> 01:12:05,854
...because something
very important is happening.

1158
01:12:07,698 --> 01:12:09,666
And that's what l wanna talk about.

1159
01:12:14,972 --> 01:12:17,236
My father is in the hospital.

1160
01:12:19,576 --> 01:12:21,043
My father...

1161
01:12:22,579 --> 01:12:23,705
...is dying.

1162
01:12:23,914 --> 01:12:26,382
This has been the hardest
challenge of my life;

1163
01:12:26,583 --> 01:12:31,520
