while my father's life slips away.

1164
01:12:32,522 --> 01:12:37,152
Any of you who have lost a parent
knows how wrenching it is...

1165
01:12:37,361 --> 01:12:41,297
...to see your mother
or your father's life ebb.

1166
01:12:42,833 --> 01:12:44,232
Excuse me.

1167
01:12:45,836 --> 01:12:47,565
This is so embarrassing for me.

1168
01:12:48,338 --> 01:12:51,933
But as upset as l was...

1169
01:12:52,276 --> 01:12:55,302
...l forged on because l knew that...

1170
01:12:55,512 --> 01:12:59,278
